{"tid":153441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薩德風波：郵輪抵濟州　3400中國客拒下船","createTime":"2017-03-12T14:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T01:43:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70a1a8398939ea52489de7c1da9ffff3b4b87e6f","tid":153441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/bkncn-20170312182415658-0312_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fbkncn-20170312182415658-0312_05011_001.html&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2ccd372b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/bkncn-20170312182415658-0312_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/photo/bkncn-20170312182415658-0312_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170312192006\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170312182415658-0312_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170312192006&h=17354c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">報道指，郵輪抵達濟州港口後，船上3400多名中國遊客拒絕下船。（網上資料圖片）</span><br />\n自南韓決定部署薩德導彈防衞系統後，中韓關係持續惡化，近日內地民間的反韓情緒亦愈來愈激烈。有日本傳媒今日引述濟州特別自治道政府消息指，昨日下午有郵輪停靠在濟州港口後，船上3400多名中國遊客集體拒絕下船，令當地負責接待的旅遊業者大失預算。 <br />\n<br />\n據報，涉事的1.1萬噸級郵輪「歌詩達賽琳娜號」（Costa Serena），載有3400多名中國某企業的員工；郵輪從日本福岡出發後，昨日下午1時許停靠濟州，原訂4小時後再出發前往中國天津港。但郵輪抵港後，船上全部中國乘客竟拒絕下船；早已在港口外等候多時的80多輛旅遊巴及導遊，都不知如何反應。有負責出入境檢疫的濟州海運組合工作人員稱，雖然近來部分乘坐郵輪來韓的中國遊客曾拒絕下船，但像這次全體拒絕下船還是首次。 <br />\n<br />\n濟州島有旅遊業者表示，自去年下半年起，當地已少了很多中國遊客到訪，故他們改向南韓本地遊客推銷較低廉的旅遊項目，「從目前來看，生意還算不錯」。當局還計劃利用南韓國內航班和郵輪的空餘座位，推出折扣優惠，以吸引更多南韓人到訪；另外在外國遊客方面，會擴展東南亞國家、日本、香港及台灣等地區的宣傳力度，以減少依賴中國客源。"},{"pid":"437a76e523d5acff6d4148853b447cf55777e46f","tid":153441,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"咁去乜鳩濟州 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96f79238da93954caf667622b3b62dc7bd739b1","tid":153441,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"報道重點係咪隻船係由福岡出發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c58add6ce07f948d35f4da682166ac84015640d","tid":153441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed680a2c0918a232c44ef1ba7626a3128f2c374","tid":153441,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"但係又肯係日本上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc15a577452ecece7f57d5c4364b1678ddc896ae","tid":153441,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"淆底, 驚比泡菜圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b779af4c2d76c31d254a123bec588f86a3795cf6","tid":153441,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報道重點係咪隻船係由福岡出發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人之前反日，而家咪又係去日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6c56884bc7bd4c82fdb286aacb25314e4372df","tid":153441,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報道重點係咪隻船係由福岡出發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人之前反日，而家咪又係去日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一單還一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1c5d7dcc6a3991ff263c03d14142187589f74b","tid":153441,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"唔明， 咁上郵輪做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9009490bbe6491